    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Fixer-upper special priced to move! This car is honestly in rough shape \u2014 it has significant wear, will need meaningful repairs, and is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer or someone looking for a project. That said, it's a real car at a real bargain price, and with the right attention it could be brought back to life. If you're handy and love a challenge, this could be your next project!",
      "price": 4500.0,
